THIS SaaS AGREEMENT ('AGREEMENT') IS ENTERED INTO BY AND BETWEEN [CLIENT] (THE 'CUSTOMER'), WITH ITS PRINCIPAL PLACE OF BUSINESS LOCATED AT [ADDRESS], AND [COMPANY NAME] (THE 'COMPANY'), WITH ITS PRINCIPAL PLACE OF BUSINESS LOCATED AT [ADDRESS].

